		"body": "Fixes #14384\r\nThe fixMigrationNames function tries to update the knex_migrations table before migrations run. The knex error event handler logged the error before the catch block could handle it silently.\r\nAdded a QueryContext with noSuchTableErrorLoggingDisabled: true to the query, preventing the error from being logged while still allowing the catch block to handle it.",
